ll-night-rave-3511159">10 月 7 日袭击</a>后，加沙地带巴勒斯坦人目前死亡人数为 29,600 人，其中约 1,410 名以色列人被杀，约 100 名以色列人质仍被哈马斯关押。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-kneecap-perform-grian-chatten-collab-better-way-to-live-and-talk-controversy-on-irelands-late-late-show-3592326">Watch Kneecap 表演 Grian Chatten 合作歌曲《Better Way To Live》并谈论爱尔兰《Late Late Show》争议的帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
布里斯托尔的 Simple Things 将 Giant Swan 从阵容中删除，“鉴于最近公开的有关其中一名成员的细节” https://www.nme.com/news/music/bristols-simple-things-remove-giant-swan-from-line-up-in-light-of-recent-details-made-public-about-one- of-the-members-3592320?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=bristols-simple-things-remove-giant-swan-from-line-up-in-light-of-recent-details-made-public-about-one-成员中的Elizabeth AubreySat, 24 Feb 2024 21:37:50 +0000 FestivalsMusic NewsNews..dance https://www.nme.com/?p=3592320 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="新媒体新闻" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “他们不适合表演”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bristols-simple-things-remove-giant-swan-from-line-up-in-light-of-recent-details-made-public-about-one-of-the-members-3592320">布里斯托尔乐队《Simple Things》将 Giant Swan 从阵容中删除的帖子“鉴于最近公开的有关其中一名成员的细节”</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="新媒体新闻" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>布里斯托尔的 Simple Things 音乐节今天（2 月 24 日）将舞蹈组合 Giant Swan 从演出阵容中删除，“鉴于最近公开的有关其中一位成员的细节”。</p><p>今天在布里斯托尔各地举行的 Simple Things 昨天（2 月 23 日）在社交媒体上宣布，已将巨天鹅从演出阵容中删除，因为“这不适合它们表演”。</p><p>它补充说，这一决定是“根据最近公开的有关乐队成员的细节”做出的。</p><p>该二人组由罗宾·斯图尔特和哈利·赖特组成，两人定于今晚结束音乐节。他们的取消是在斯图尔特的前合伙人在公开帖子中对他提出指控之后进行的。</p><p>斯图尔特在社交媒体上分享了一份声明，他在其中写道：“鉴于与我个人生活有关的问题，为自己提供平台是不合适的，因此我们将不再在 Simple Things 上表演……这不是我们所采取的做法。”在我讨论如何从这里开始时，希望您能理解。” <em>NME</em>已联系 Giant Swan 征求意见。</p><p> Scaler 乐队取代了阵容中的二人组。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C3smjk7s0op/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.00